org.eclipse.scada.configuration.world.osgi

Interface PullEvents

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Documentable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PullEventsImpl

    public interface PullEvents
extends Documentable
    A representation of the model object 'Pull Events'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Jdbc Driver Name
    • Jdbc Properties
    • Job Interval
    • Custom Select Sql
    • Custom Delete Sql

    See Also:
    OsgiPackage.getPullEvents()
